      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Shun-Chin Hsu</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"http://www.iis.sinica.edu.tw/Conference/ICGA2005/icga/img/2005_09_04/slides/IMG_0264.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/5/58/Schsu.JPG\" width=\"200\" height=\"271\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Schsu.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Shun-Chin Hsu <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Shun-Chin Hsu</b>,<br />\na Taiwanese computer scientiest and Professor at the Department of Information Engineering and Computer Science <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> at the <a href=\"/National_Taiwan_University\" title=\"National Taiwan University\">National Taiwan University</a>. His research interests covers <a href=\"/Games\" title=\"Games\">Games</a>, specially <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Chinese Chess</a> and <a href=\"/Go\" title=\"Go\">Computer Go</a>, <a href=\"/Retrograde_Analysis\" title=\"Retrograde Analysis\">Retrograde Analysis</a> for Chinese Chess <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a>, and various <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">search</a> issues. Shun-Chin Hsu is co-author of various strong programs, successfully competing at <a href=\"/ICGA\" title=\"ICGA\">ICGA</a> Tournaments <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> of <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Chinese Chess</a>, <a href=\"/Go\" title=\"Go\">Go</a> and <a href=\"/Connect6\" title=\"Connect6\">Connect6</a>. Along with <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a> and <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tsan-Cheng_Su&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tsan-Cheng Su (page does not exist)\">Tsan-Cheng Su</a>, Shun-Chin Hsu is author of the <a href=\"/Othello\" title=\"Othello\">Othello</a> program <i>Tower of Othello</i>, which won silver at <a href=\"/index.php?title=TAAI_2013&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"TAAI 2013 (page does not exist)\">TAAI 2013</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> and the gold medal (shared) at <a href=\"/index.php?title=TCGA_2014&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"TCGA 2014 (page does not exist)\">TCGA 2014</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Programs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Programs</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Chinese_Chess\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chinese Chess</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Go\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Go</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Connect6\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Connect6</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Othello\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Othello</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#1985_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1985 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#1990_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1990 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#1995_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1995 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-14\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Programs\">Programs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shun-Chin_Hsu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Programs\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chinese_Chess\"><a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Chinese Chess</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shun-Chin_Hsu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Chinese Chess\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Elephant_(Xiangqi)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Elephant (Xiangqi) (page does not exist)\">Elephant</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=ELP&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"ELP (page does not exist)\">ELP</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Contemplation&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Contemplation (page does not exist)\">Contemplation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Chimo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Chimo (page does not exist)\">Chimo</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Go\"><a href=\"/Go\" title=\"Go\">Go</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shun-Chin_Hsu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Go\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> Dragon 2</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/program.php?id=161\">Archimage</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Connect6\"><a href=\"/Connect6\" title=\"Connect6\">Connect6</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shun-Chin_Hsu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Connect6\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/program.php?id=233\">EVG</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Othello\"><a href=\"/Othello\" title=\"Othello\">Othello</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shun-Chin_Hsu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Othello\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> Tower of Othello</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shun-Chin_Hsu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1985_...\">1985 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shun-Chin_Hsu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 1985 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a>, D.H. Huang (<b>1985</b>). <i>Design and Implementation of a Chinese Chess Knowledge Base.</i> Proceedings of NCS, pp. 505-509. (in Chinese)</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1990_...\">1990 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shun-Chin_Hsu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 1990 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>1990</b>). <i>Introduction to Computer Chess and Computer Chinese Chess.</i> Journal of Computer, Vol. 2, No. 2, pp. 1-8. (in Chinese)</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>1991</b>). <i>Searching Techniques of Computer Game Playing</i>. Bulletin of the College of Engineering, <a href=\"/National_Taiwan_University\" title=\"National Taiwan University\">National Taiwan University</a>, 51:17–31 </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a>, D.Y. Liu (<b>1991</b>). <i>The Design and Construction of the Computer Go Program DRAGON 2.</i> Computer Go, No. 16, pp. 3-14.</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Kuo-Ming_Tsao&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Kuo-Ming Tsao (page does not exist)\">Kuo-Ming Tsao</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jen-Hsuan_Li&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jen-Hsuan Li (page does not exist)\">Jen-Hsuan Li</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>1991</b>). <i>Design and Implementation of a Chinese Chess Program</i>. <a href=\"/2nd_Computer_Olympiad#Workshop\" title=\"2nd Computer Olympiad\">Heuristic Programming in AI 2</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Kuo-Ming_Tsao&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Kuo-Ming Tsao (page does not exist)\">Kuo-Ming Tsao</a> (<b>1991</b>). <i>Design and Implementation of an Opening Game Knowledge-Base System for Computer Chinese Chess.</i> Bulletin of the College of Engineering, N.T.U., No. 53 (in Chinese)</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeng-Chi_Yan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jeng-Chi Yan (page does not exist)\">Jeng-Chi Yan</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Hongsen_Chang&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Hongsen Chang (page does not exist)\">Hongsen Chang</a> (<b>1994</b>). <i>Design and Implementation of a Computer Go Program ARCHIMAGE 1.1.</i> Journal of Information Sciences and Engineering, Vol. 10</li>\n<li> Y. J. Hwang, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>1994</b>). <i>Design and Implementation of a Position Judgement System for Computer Go Programs</i>. Bulleting of the College of Engineering, N.T.U., No. 62</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1995_...\">1995 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shun-Chin_Hsu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: 1995 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeng-Chi_Yan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jeng-Chi Yan (page does not exist)\">Jeng-Chi Yan</a>, W.J. Chen, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i>Design and implementation of a heuristic beginning game system for computer Go</i>. JCIS’98, Vol. 1, pp. 381-384.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shun-Chin_Hsu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Haw-ren_Fang\" title=\"Haw-ren Fang\">Haw-ren Fang</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-45579-5_7\">Construction of Chinese Chess Endgame Databases by Retrograde Analysis</a></i>. <a href=\"/CG_2000\" title=\"CG 2000\">CG 2000</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeng-Chi_Yan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jeng-Chi Yan (page does not exist)\">Jeng-Chi Yan</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>Research and Design of Killer Moves Generator</i>. Proceedings of TAAI 2001  (in Chinese)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeng-Chi_Yan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jeng-Chi Yan (page does not exist)\">Jeng-Chi Yan</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>A Positional Judgment System for computer Go</i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_9\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 9\">Advances in Computer Games 9</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>ELP wins Chinese Chess tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#24_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 24, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/6th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"6th Computer Olympiad\">6th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i>ELP wins Chinese Chess tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#25_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 25, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/7th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"7th Computer Olympiad\">7th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Haw-ren_Fang\" title=\"Haw-ren Fang\">Haw-ren Fang</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-40031-8_18\">Indefinite Sequence of Moves in Chinese Chess Endgames</a></i>. <a href=\"/CG_2002\" title=\"CG 2002\">CG 2002</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>ZMBL wins Chinese Chess tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#26_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 26, No. 4</a> &#160;» <a href=\"/8th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"8th Computer Olympiad\">8th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Haw-ren_Fang\" title=\"Haw-ren Fang\">Haw-ren Fang</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ilk.uvt.nl/icga/journal/contents/content27-1.htm#INFCHESS\">Checking Indefinitely in Chinese-Chess Endgames</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#27_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 27, No. 1</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_C